13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Ideal vazn kalkulyatori bir nechta ilmiy formulalar bo'yicha tavsiya etilgan tana massasi diapazonini aniqlaydi: Lorents, Brok, Devayn, Robinson va JSST (TMI 18,5-24,9). Natija bo'y, jins va tana tuzilishi turiga bog'liq. O'zbekiston aholisi uchun, bu yerda erkaklar o'rtacha bo'yi — 172 sm, ayollar — 160 sm, kalkulyator shaxsiylashtirilgan tavsiyalar beradi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash formulalari: Brok (oddiy): erkaklar — bo'y(sm) − 100, ayollar — bo'y(sm) − 110. Lorents: erkaklar uchun — (bo'y − 100) − (bo'y − 150) / 4; ayollar uchun — (bo'y − 100) − (bo'y − 150) / 2. Devayn: erkaklar — 50 + 2,3 × (bo'y/2,54 − 60); ayollar — 45,5 + 2,3 × (bo'y/2,54 − 60). JSST: bo'y(m)² × 18,5 (minimum) dan bo'y(m)² × 24,9 (maksimum) gacha."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonning o'rtacha erkagi (172 sm) uchun misol: Brok: 72 kg, Lorents: 66,5 kg, Devayn: 68,5 kg, JSST: 54,7-73,5 kg. Tavsiya etilgan diapazon: 63-72 kg. O'rtacha ayol (160 sm) uchun: Brok: 50 kg, Lorents: 55 kg, Devayn: 54,5 kg, JSST: 47,4-63,7 kg. Optimal: 52-60 kg."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Ideal vazn — mo'ljal, mutlaq ko'rsatkich emas. Haqiqiy sog'lom vazniga mushak massasi (sportchilar past yog' foizida ko'proq tortadilar), yosh (50 yoshdan keyin +5-10% ruxsat etiladi), tana tuzilishi turi (astenik, normostenik, giperstenik), genetik xususiyatlar ta'sir qiladi. O'zbekiston aholisi asosan normostenik tana tuzilishiga ega bo'lgani uchun formulalar eng aniq natija beradi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Ideal vazn kalkulyatorini TMI kalkulyatori va kaloriya kalkulyatori bilan birgalikda ishlating — bu to'liq baholash va ovqatlanish rejasini ishlab chiqish imkonini beradi. Bo'y va jinsni kiriting — kalkulyator barcha formulalar bo'yicha tavsiya etilgan diapazonni, o'rtacha qiymatni va joriy vazningizdan og'ishni ko'rsatadi."}]]}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Ko'p beriladigan savollar"}],["$","$L18",null,{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card px-4","children":[["$","$L19","0",{"value":"faq-0","children":[["$","$L1a",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"Ideal vaznni qanday hisoblash mumkin?"}],["$","$L1b",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"Brok, Lorents, Devayn formulalari yoki TMI 18,5-24,9 orqali. Kalkulyator barcha usullarni qo'llaydi va o'rtacha natijani ko'rsatadi."}]}]]}],"$L1c","$L1d","$L1e","$L1f"]}]]}],"$L20"]}]
